    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">6. China Manufacturing: CCC QR Codes &amp; Regulatory Reset</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6"><strong>China's CNCA Announcement No. 27 of 2025</strong> mandates QR-coded CCC marks for all power banks, triggering the largest regulatory consolidation of Shenzhen's charging accessory manufacturing sector in a decade. Two major changes reshape the landscape for OEM/ODM buyers sourcing from the Greater Bay Area.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
