        <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-3 text-sm">CCC Traceability QR Codes</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3">China's CNCA <strong>Announcement No. 27 of 2025</strong> requires all power banks and portable power sources to carry a QR code alongside the CCC mark. Scanning reveals the certificate number, manufacturer name, model, and certificate validity status.</p>
