            <td class="p-3"><span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full">MANDATORY</span></td>
            <td class="p-3 text-slate-600 text-xs">All new charger designs must certify under PD 3.2</td>
            <td class="p-3 text-slate-600 text-xs">Non-compliance = no USB-IF cert, no EU market access</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-t border-slate-200">
